# THE BIG ONE: a full yellow belt (15/s) of electronic circuits.
# ~107 machines: every circuit machine is 3-cable-arm-bound, every cable machine
# output-arm-bound; copper needs two input belts; the output belt runs at 100%.
input copper : copper-plate
input iron : iron-plate
assembler cable : copper-cable
assembler circuit : electronic-circuit
output chips @ 15/s

copper -> cable
cable -> circuit
iron -> circuit
circuit -> chips
